    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and care. The exterior paint maintains a brilliant luster, showing only minor, superficial road wear consistent with responsible ownership. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has been kept in a smoke-free environment; the seats are firm and supportive with no tears, and all electronic features\u2014including the infotainment system and climate control\u2014are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine is responsive and quiet, benefiting from regular synthetic oil changes and a documented maintenance history. The transmission shifts smoothly through every gear, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. With a set of high-tread tires and a clean title, this car is mechanically sound and aesthetically pleasing, offering a premium driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
